a provisional release so fast.

122
00:11:13.785 --> 00:11:16.747
The governor had a PR nightmare last year
with the Willis execution.

123
00:11:16.830 --> 00:11:19.374
so they cut corners.
It's fucking politics.

124
00:11:19.458 --> 00:11:21.126
